overview:
WELCOME TO ILLUMINATED DESIGN GROUP We are committed to providing quality graphic design, web design and logo design and branding, utilizing a combination of organic and digital elements woven with thoughtful copy and stimulating graphics. We recognize the importance of a comprehensive approach, recognizing the importance of color, space, line and texture.

We proudly provide our professional graphic design, logo design, corporate branding, web design and print design in Newbury Park, Thousand oaks, Westlake Village, Camarillo, Oxnard, Santa Barbara and throughout Ventura County.
